EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0800Z TO 2100Z DAILY
   13 THRU 19 MAY IN AREAS:
   A. WITHIN 85 MILES OF 57-20.3N 010-03.5W.
   B. WITHIN 70 MILES OF 58-04.2N 010-27.7W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 OR
   PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 192200Z MAY 19.
